# Web UI: tech stack

- **Styles**: always **SCSS**. Use `<style lang="scss">` in Vue components (no `scoped`). Rely on **SCSS nesting** and a **root class** per component (e.g. `.dashboard-page`, `.queue-detail`) so styles stay local without scoped.
- **Scripts**: always **TypeScript**. Use `<script setup lang="ts">` in Vue; no JavaScript.
- **Templates**: use component tags in **kebab-case** (e.g. `<confirm-modal>`, `<message-modal>`, `<modal>`), not PascalCase.
